remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities>類別會擴充<xref:System.Web.HttpBrowserCapabilities>類別。 <xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities>類別提供了大量的唯讀屬性，可提供瀏覽器物件的功能字典的型別安全存取。  
  
 您可以使用的瀏覽器屬性<xref:System.Web.HttpRequest>物件指向的執行個體<xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities>物件，然後可以用來讀取要求的瀏覽器和裝置的功能。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 頁面在載入期間，<xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities>物件取得的功能，透過<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase.Browser%2A>先前所討論的屬性。 <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase.PreferredRenderingMime%2A>和<xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase.ScreenCharactersWidth%2A>屬性<xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities>物件傳回至瀏覽器的報表上設定屬性<xref:System.Web.HttpResponse>物件和也以程式設計方式設定`Text`頁面上某些控制項的屬性。  
  
```csharp  
<%@ Page Inherits="System.Web.UI.MobileControls.MobilePage"   
    Language="c#" %>  
<script language="c#" runat="server">  
public void Page_Load(Object sender, EventArgs e)  
{  
    System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities currentCapabilities;  
    MobileCapabilities currentCapabilities =   
        (MobileCapabilities)Request.Browser;  
    // Programatically find the mobile capabilities without using   
    // DeviceSpecific Filters.  
    if(currentCapabilities.PreferredRenderingMIME=="text/html")  
    {  
        Label2.Text = "You are using an html supported device.";  
    }  
    else if(currentCapabilities.PreferredRenderingMIME ==   
        "text/vnd.wap.wml")  
    {  
        Label2.Text = "You are using a wml supported device.";  
    }  
    Label1.Text = "Screen Width (chars): " +   
        currentCapabilities.ScreenCharactersWidth;  
 }  
 </script>  
 <Mobile:Form runat="server" id=frmTemplate >  
      <mobile:label ID="Label1" runat="server" />  
      <mobile:label ID="Label2" runat="server" />  
 </Mobile:Form>  
```
